msgid ""
"Desert Fighters make up the bulk of the Elven military in Wesnoth. They are "
"trained in both sword and bow, though like most of their kin, they prefer "
"swordplay to archery. These Elves are deft of foot, and fight best in the "
"open sands."
msgstr ""
"I combattenti del deserto formano la massa dei militari elfici di Wesnoth. "
"Sono addestrati sia con la spada che con l'arco, sebbene come molti della "
"loro gente preferiscano la scherma all'arcieria. Questi elfi sono svelti di "
"piede, e combattono al meglio nelle sabbie aperte."

#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Desert_Hero.cfg:4
#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Kaleh_Hero.cfg:4
msgid "Desert Hero"
msgstr "Eroe del deserto"

#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Desert_Hero.cfg:48
#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Kaleh_Hero.cfg:49
msgid ""
"Desert Heroes focus on individual performance on the battlefield, having "
"tweaked their combat skills to the very maximum. Desert Heroes prefer "
"fighting at close range with the sword, but also have some skill with the "
"bow."
msgstr ""
"Gli eroi del deserto si dedicano alla ricerca del risultato individuale sul "
"campo di battaglia, avendo affinato le capacità di combattimento al massimo "
"livello. Gli eroi del deserto preferiscono combattere a breve raggio con la "
"spada, ma sono discretamente abili anche nell'uso dell'arco."

#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Desert_Horseman.cfg:4
msgid "Desert Horseman"
msgstr ""

#: Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/Desert_Horseman.cfg:50
msgid ""
"Trading speed for heavier arms and armament, Elvish Horseman delight in "
"riding into danger instead of away from it. The open sands are much more "
"suited towards mounted combat than their old forests were, and through the "
"generations the Elves have greatly increased their equestrian skills. The "
"mounted speed and agility allows them to get in more strikes than most "
"fighters"
msgstr ""

